rows.label: bf04110100_0040
rows.name:
I'm sorry about Hikari-chan. She gets very
confused when she's just woken up...

rows.label: bf04110100_0070
rows.name:
No! I didn't do anything weird!
Not a thing!

rows.label: bf04110100_0080
rows.name:
No...? It was more Hikari-chan I was
worrying about.

rows.label: bf04110100_0100
rows.name: I guess...she did throw a thing or two.

rows.label: bf04110100_0110
rows.name: Oh no. So that was where that came from.

rows.label: bf04110100_0120
rows.name: I'm sorry. Did it hurt a lot?

rows.label: bf04110100_0130
rows.name:
N-no! Not at all!
Really, I'm fine!

rows.label: bf04110100_0140
rows.name:
Are you sure?
Honestly...my head is still a little painful.

rows.label: bf04110100_0170
rows.name:
We need a little romance
in our lives, too, eh?
